item.title: University of Girona
item.description: The Girona Underwater Vision and Robotics research lab (cirs.udg.edu), as part of the ViCOROB Institute from the University of Girona, Spain, has a strong experience in the design and development of hovering AUV prototypes with high-resolution image mapping capabilities.

item.description: ABOUT LABUST: The LABUST origins can be traced back to late 1960s when the research group was formed at the University of Zagreb Faculty of Electrical Engineering (UNIZG-FER) and at the association of shipbuilding industry „Jadranbrod“ in Zagreb.
